item.dc:creator: Jamie Corstorphine
item.description: Our honey is proudly sourced from the pristine green plains and native forests of New Zealand. Our minimal processing technique […]
item.content:encoded: Our honey is proudly sourced from the pristine green plains and native forests of New Zealand. Our minimal processing technique allows the honey to retain its natural enzymes, pollen, and antioxidants. MGO is expressed as mg/kg. The UMF rating system independently certifies the natural components found in manuka honey to assure potency, purity, authenticity, and freshness.
